<TEI.2><text><body><div1 type="alphabetic letter" n="F" org="uniform" sample="complete"><entryFree key="Flash1" type="main" opt="n"><orth extent="full" opt="n">Flash,</orth> subst. 1) a burst of light, a sudden blaze: <cit><quote>lightning f.</quote> <bibl n="shak. tit 2.1.3" default="NO" valid="yes">Tit. II, 1, 3</bibl></cit>. <bibl n="shak. jc 1.3.52" default="NO" valid="yes">Caes. I, 3, 52</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. per 3.1.6" default="NO" valid="yes">Per. III, 1, 6</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. cym 4.2.270" default="NO" valid="yes">Cymb. IV, 2, 270</bibl>.<lb />2) a sudden burst or outbreak of high spirits: <cit><quote>the f. and outbreak of a fiery mind,</quote> <bibl n="shak. ham 2.1.33" default="NO" valid="yes">Hml. II, 1, 33</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>your --es of merriment,</quote> <bibl n="shak. ham 5.1.210" default="NO" valid="yes">V, 1, 210</bibl></cit>.
</entryFree></div1></body></text></TEI.2>